node.text:
Guysss I  am SO excited to announce my partnership with @chefgood 

Nutrition is the key 🔑 to long term results. Through my partnership with @chefgood, Tammy Fit aims to offer convenience without compromise. 

You can now shop Chefgood meals that align with your health and fitness goals in the Tammy Fit app, just head to the nutrition page. Or you can shop through the link in my bio. 

And the meals are sooo yummy, if I’m short on time they are my go-to. They are hand crafted, with natural ingredients using only fresh local produce. 

Enter the code TAMMY20 to get 20% off your first order (new customers only). Valid until 04/08/2021.

#chefgood #tammyfit
